Part 4: Networking & Package Management
Very important for Cloud Engineers 🌐
Networking Commands
Copy code

ip a
ifconfig
ping google.com
netstat -tulnp
ss -tulnp
traceroute google.com
curl http://example.com
wget http://example.com/file.zip
Package Management (Ubuntu)
Copy code

apt update
apt upgrade
apt install nginx
apt remove nginx
Package Management (RHEL/CentOS)
Copy code

yum install httpd
yum update
dnf install nginx
